snippet.title: Fort Triumph - Gameplay Trailer (V0.7.2)
snippet.description:
Coming soon to Steam Early Access. 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/612570

A fresh collection of gameplay footage with an Early Access candidate build (March 2018). 

Includes our hot new crypt environment, multiple new foes to defeat, and a taste of our world map gameplay.
